Key walks out of the CR chamber. She looks around a bit confused, and then 
goes back out to the battle. She tells herself to remember to thank whoever 
had saved her while she shoots at Hades.

Blue Stinger opens her eyes. She stands up, trying to ignore the pain in her 
wing, and walks back to the battle.

Sona wakes up as the sword hits her neck and almost cuts her head off. She 
rolls to the side, transforming into beast mode.

Antagony falls into a boulder as all the rockets and shots hit her. She goes 
unconscious.
